If the turn is **only** a narrow code edit unrelated to sync/QA/deploy, you may defer the re-read until the topic shifts — but you **must** load this topology section (below) before any operational or architectural statement about relay, entitlement, or test devices.

After re-reading, **state internally** (do not paste a checklist to the user unless they ask): machines, roles, URLs, and what you still need to verify with tools.

